export function getRelatedProducts(productId) {
  const product = ProductData.find(p => p.id === productId);
  if (!product) return [];
  return ProductData.filter(p => p.category === product.category && p.id !== productId);
}

export function getRelatedProducts(productId) {
  const product = ProductData.find(p => p.id === productId);
  if (!product) return [];

  return ProductData.filter(p => p.category === product.category && p.id !== productId);
}
